## Limitations

The research was limited by the availability of detailed historical records and the potential bias in sources that focus predominantly on the positive aspects of the empires. Additionally, the reliance on secondary sources may not fully capture the complexity of the economic systems within these empires. Further research using primary historical documents would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the factors contributing to their prosperity.

